### Register a new user
POST https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### Login
POST https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Create a brand (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brandName": "Nike"
}

###

### Get all brands
GET https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/brands

###

### Update a brand (Admin only)
PUT https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/brands/PUT_BRAND_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brandName": "Adidas"
}

###

### Delete a brand (Admin only)
DELETE https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/brands/PUT_BRAND_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### Get paginated products by brand
GET https://e-commerce-api-heyc.onrender.com/brands/PUT_BRAND_ID_HERE/products?page=1&limit=5